snippet.title: Bluetooth BiPlanes | Walkthrough (Java Game)
snippet.description:
00:00 Intro
00:12 Easy
03:29 Medium
07:17 Hard
12:53 Expert

BT Biplanes is one of the best Java-games, that has Bluetooth multiplayer mode. Flying a small aircraft you have to destroy the enemy piloting the second plane. The game has a perfectly realized physics of flight, which allows you to make dizzying aerobatics!

Developers: Morpheme Wireless
Released: 2004
